Compile and Run the Program Using these Commands
------------------------------------------------------------------------

1.pi-mystery.cu

Single precision :

Compile	: nvcc -O3 pi-mystery.cu
Run	: ./a.out

Double precision :

Compile	: nvcc -O3 -D DP pi-mystery.cu
Run	: ./a.out

------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.pi-currand.cu
  ============

Single precision :

Compile	: nvcc -O3 -Xcompiler -fopenmp -lgomp pi-curand.cu
Run	: ./a.out <No of Threads>

Double precision :

Compile	: nvcc -O3 -D DP -Xcompiler -fopenmp -lgomp pi-curand.cu
Run	: ./a.out <No of Threads>

------------------------------------------------------------------------
3.pi-myrand.cu

Single precision :

Compile	: nvcc -O3 pi-myrand.cu
Run	: ./a.out

Double precision :

Compile	: nvcc -O3 -D DP pi-myrand.cu
Run	: ./a.out

------------------------------------------------------------------------
4.pi-curand-thrust.cu

Single precision :

Compile	: nvcc -O3 pi-curand-thrust.cu
Run	: ./a.out

Double precision :

Compile	: nvcc -O3 -D DP pi-curand-thrust.cu
Run	: ./a.out

------------------------------------------------------------------------

